title: Mark Rothko Untitled, c.1958 Holiday Cards
description:
An elegant work of art is a wonderful way to send your good wishes this, and every holiday season. These beautiful holiday cards & envelopes are made in the USA . Cards are printed on the finest quality, environmentally friendly stock. Box of 12 cards of one design with envelopes.

Mark Rothko (1903-1970). Untitled, c.1958. National Gallery of Art
  • Dimensions: Box 5.5 x 7.5 x 1 in, Card 5 x 7 in.
  • Materials: Matte gold foil box with acetate lid, environmentally friendly stock paper
  • Inside Message: Wishing you Peace and Joy this Holiday Season
